MELLO: So when I was watching this show I couldn't help but think of mello yello soda every time I heard this guy's name. Seriously I couldn't. Aside from that though this was another pretty forgettable character. He was apparently the leader of a Mafia like group- and they were pretty successful. He actually gets his claws on the Death Note for a bit. But like the rest of Arc 2, he goes no where. Honestly, no real reason for him to be in the story aside from 'buliding (if you can call it that)' the backstory for this part of this show.\
