\9There is also a great blend of fantasy that is mixed into this anime with the involvement of a Shinigami that comes with the Death Note and it works out really well.\
\9Another major pro to this anime is Light relationship with his father who his on the team of detectives bent on stopping Light.\
\9Death Note is most certainly a major accomplishment in the anime genre and is definitely a masterpiece.\
Downsides\
